title: Cirque du Soleil - Corteo Soundtrack
description:
Cirque du Soleil - Corteo soundtrack + EXTRA BONUS

I have included all the tracks from the original soundtrack with all the ID tags OK and album artwork, so for those who have ipods it should all be organized!

The extra track I have included is the one where, in the show, everyone sorrounds three performers who jump on a see saw, this because it has a cool rythm and it is not included on the soundtrack. I ripped this bit from the DVD. I named this track trampoline.
